    <item>
      <title>哈里斯和沃尔兹计划在辩论后访问竞争激烈的摇摆州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/harris-walz-plan-post-debate-tour-of-swing-states-in-tight-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将在周二与唐纳德·特朗普的辩论后前往仍然激烈的战场州，一项民意调查显示，这位前总统在全国范围内领先，许多选民表示他们需要更多地了解哈里斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/harris-walz-plan-post-debate-tour-of-swing-states-in-tight-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:04:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>坦桑尼亚总统下令调查选举前绑架事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/tanzania-president-orders-probe-into-pre-election-abductions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[坦桑尼亚总统萨米亚·苏鲁胡·哈桑下令对该国即将举行的选举前政治人物和政府批评人士的绑架事件进行调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/tanzania-president-orders-probe-into-pre-election-abductions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:03:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院对阿富汗撤军的调查将延续至大选之后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/house-probe-into-afghanistan-pullout-to-extend-beyond-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责调查的一位议员表示，众议院共和党人将把对美国撤军阿富汗的为期两年的调查延长至周一发布的报告之后，并持续到 11 月“大选结束后很长一段时间”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/house-probe-into-afghanistan-pullout-to-extend-beyond-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:05:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿尔及利亚领导人特本在提前选举中以压倒性优势再次当选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/algerian-president-wins-by-a-landslide-in-initial-vote-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔及利亚总统阿卜杜勒马吉德·特本轻松赢得第二个任期，成为这个欧佩克国家的领导人。批评人士称，此次选举比预期提前举行，是为了排挤任何强劲竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/algerian-president-wins-by-a-landslide-in-initial-vote-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界主要碳排放国称新气候谈判取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/world-s-top-carbon-emitters-cite-progress-in-new-climate-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在北京举行的为期三天的会谈中，美国和中国谈判代表讨论了遏制森林砍伐和减少严重的全球变暖污染等共同目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/world-s-top-carbon-emitters-cite-progress-in-new-climate-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 15:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
